    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but it feels like the term is used differently depending on who u ask. like, some people use it to talk about actual lies/misinformation, but then other politicians use it just to dismiss any reporting they don't like. do you think there's a difference between real fake news and people just using it as a political weapon?",
